messages.message: yea I think Paul’s right here — given the insanely positive reception @Hari and I got from almost all of the SC groups we chatted with and how excited they were for instabase to rollout, we should focus on supporting those use cases and just ignoring this group going forward. Positive results from many, many other groups will (and already are I’m sure) speak for themselves. Also — We might accidentally end up amplifying their message if we focus on it enough to try to exclude them from the license.
